message: MacBook Air A1465 didn?t charge with a tried 2 chargers some Time it works some it didn?t check power bench it works fine. Changed the dc board still same problem. Any advise

title: 820-00164-b
message: I have changed the U7090 Ic still same problem but work with power bench but not with chargers tried a few chargers no luck

title: 820-00164-b
message:
Looks like leakage on input stage; usually D7012, or Q7180.
But need some voltage readings, or diode mode, to confirm which is.

Post Q7010 voltages and R7012 exact value; ohm scale, measured onboard.

title: 820-00164-b
message: Hi it was R7012 + D7012 cheers for all the help

title: 820-00164-b
message: Inspect L8304 for high resistance or damage.
